Y16 Sum of Digits

Given an integer N, Find the sum of individual digits of it.

Input Format

Single integer represents N.

Constraints

0<= N <=10,00,00,000

Output Format

Sum of Individual digits of a number.

Sample Input 0

123
Sample Output 0

6
Sample Input 1

1122033
Sample Output 1

12

Solution:

#include <stdio.h>
#include <string.h>
#include <math.h>
#include <stdlib.h>

int main() {
    long long int a;
int count=0,digit;
scanf("%lld",&a);
while (a > 0) {
 int digit = a % 10;
    count=count+digit;
a /= 10;
}
    printf("%d",count);
}

